{"tid":1153262,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西媒：巴塞高層認為華維迪應離任 將進行決議","createTime":"2019-05-13T13:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T13:37:05.000Z","uid":34571,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a1985b610d58f19df52b3137d7fbddc489b853e4","tid":1153262,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"直播吧5月13日訊 向《世界體育報》供稿的加泰記者洛倫特（Marcal Lorente）通過電台節目《Sin Concesiones》透露，當地時間今天下午，巴塞高層將召開董事會討論華維迪的未來。<br />\n<br />\n  據悉，巴塞大多數高層認為，華維迪不應該繼續執教，一線隊主管佩普-塞古拉也應該被解僱。<br />\n<br />\n  記者透露，今天董事會上高層將具體討論以上問題，但即便決議通過，具體的結果也會等到西班牙盃決賽之後再確定。"},{"pid":"682193833654240c36c5727b9670ec9891c2373c","tid":1153262,"uid":66839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:29:12.000Z","msg":"終於捨得走"},{"pid":"e2eb8e1dd95a88347d72c2a0fb39ad03b9337b02","tid":1153262,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:29:14.000Z","msg":"想搵邊個教先"},{"pid":"608060a78ad2303cc507818919ac6f4cd4b331b9","tid":1153262,"uid":71020,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e2eb8e1dd95a88347d72c2a0fb39ad03b9337b02","tid":1153262,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:29:14.000Z","msg":"想搵邊個教先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:29:40.000Z","msg":"問小花"},{"pid":"d4b143973858cd2a42635a8690f765f3c53e4e0e","tid":1153262,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"哥狗返巴塞啦<br />\n阻撚住晒"},{"pid":"e9c5d9be31b203aafdbec0f48b7cae376bae8851","tid":1153262,"uid":20563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:31:14.000Z","msg":"又可以搵拼圖"},{"pid":"b39248dc6c1562421f3559b4093dadb7089752b2","tid":1153262,"uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e2eb8e1dd95a88347d72c2a0fb39ad03b9337b02","tid":1153262,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:29:14.000Z","msg":"想搵邊個教先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:32:49.0